Class TaxonomyPartitionHelper

java.lang.Object
  oracle.apps.fnd.applseed.rt.extract.util.taxonomy.AbstractPartitionHelper
      oracle.apps.fnd.applseed.rt.extract.util.taxonomy.TaxonomyPartitionHelper
All Implemented Interfaces:
PartitionHelper
Direct Known Subclasses:
ApplicationIdHelperImpl, ModuleIdHelperImpl
public abstract class TaxonomyPartitionHelper
extends AbstractPartitionHelper

This abstract class handles partitioning using a Taxonomy attribute, currently either ModuleId or ApplicationId. The HelperImpl classes implement specific functionality for the attributes, like retrieving taxomomy module rows, and getting the transposed display name.

thePartitionKeyMap

protected PartitionKeyMap thePartitionKeyMap
The list of taxonomy partition key values found in the database. This maps the partition key id (ModuleId or AppId value) from the db to its taxonomy data (name, type, parent, etc)
